INSERT INTO "content_record" VALUES(8,'Massachusetts Institute of Technology','MIT also places among the top five in many overall rankings of universities (see right) and rankings based on students'' revealed preferences. For several years, U.S. News & World Report, the QS World University Rankings, and the Academic Ranking of World Universities have ranked MIT''s School of Engineering first, as did the 1995 National Research Council report.[225] In the same lists, MIT''s strongest showings apart from in engineering are in computer science, the natural sciences','','','','','https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/59/MIT_Walker_Memorial.jpg/1280px-MIT_Walker_Memorial.jpg',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KIop1hxFliQ',NULL,1,0,0,0,NULL,3,'2020-07-15 17:34:42');
INSERT INTO "content_record" VALUES(9,'Stanford University','Stanford University, officially Leland Stanford Junior University,[12] is a private research university in Stanford, California. Stanford is known for its academic achievements, wealth, location within Silicon Valley, and selectivity; it is ranked as one of the world''s top universities.
INSERT INTO "content_record" VALUES(10,'Harvard University','Harvard University is a private Ivy League research university in Cambridge, Massachusetts. Established in 1636 and named for its first benefactor, clergyman John Harvard, Harvard is the oldest institution of higher learning in the United States[7] and among the most prestigious in the world.','','','','','https://content.techgig.com/thumb/msid-75120114,width-1200,height-900,resizemode-4/75120114.jpg',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C5pKtnmHTxg',NULL,0,0,0,0,NULL,3,'2020-07-15 17:34:42');
INSERT INTO "content_record" VALUES(11,'The University of Texas at Dallas','In 2019, U.S. News and World Report in Best Colleges ranked UTD at 129th nationally and 61st among public universities.[63][64] The 2017 Academic Ranking of World Universities placed UTD at 71st–99th in the United States. Washington Monthly''s 2015 Annual College and University Rankings placed UTD at 99th in the United States. Kiplinger''s Personal Finance magazine''s 100 Best Values in Public Colleges 2016 ranked UTD at 33rd in value for in-state residents and 38th for out-of-state students.','','','','','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcT1Sn773n_7rdyHdy_zlR2ATx8reUqp27jnBA&usqp=CAU',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lSpANsEzbM0',NULL,1,0,1,0,NULL,3,'2020-07-15 17:34:42');
