INSERT INTO "content_record" VALUES(14,'University of Southern California','USC was ranked 22nd in U.S. News & World Report''s 2020 annual ranking of national universities.[132] In the Niche Best Colleges rankings, USC ranked 19th overall for 2020 based on academics and quality of student life.[133] USC is ranked 32nd among national universities in the U.S. and 55th in the world by the Academic Ranking of World Universities, and 13th (tied with seven other universities) among national universities by The Center for Measuring University Performance.[134] In 2015, USA Toda','','','','','https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/191112141459-01-university-of-southern-california-campus-file-super-tease.jpg',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eERe0-E4Zpg',NULL,0,0,0,0,NULL,3,'2020-07-15 17:34:42');
INSERT INTO "content_record" VALUES(15,'Trinity College Dublin','Trinity College Dublin - The University of Dublin is an international university, steeped in history with a reputation for excellence in education, research and innovation. Trinity is Ireland’s leading university and is ranked 108th in the world1 and has been inspiring generations of brilliant thinkers for over 400 years.
INSERT INTO "content_record" VALUES(16,'University College Dublin','University College Dublin (commonly referred to as UCD; Irish: Coláiste na hOllscoile, Baile Átha Cliath) is a research university in Dublin, Ireland, and a member institution of the National University of Ireland. It has over 1,482 academic staff and 32,000 students,[2] and it is Ireland''s largest university, based on 2017/18 student enrolments. UCD originates in a body founded in 1854, which opened as the Catholic University of Ireland on the Feast of Saint Malachy and with John Henry Newman a','','','','','https://www.findamasters.com/bespoke-pages/custom-pages/bpid4879/img2019624858.jpg',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=43RmIdPn2eA',NULL,0,0,0,0,NULL,15,'2020-07-15 17:34:42');
INSERT INTO "content_record" VALUES(17,'University of Vienna','The University of Vienna was founded by Duke Rudolph IV in 1365. It is the oldest university in the German-speaking world and one of the largest in Central Europe.  With 178 degree programmes, 40 university continuing education and training programmes and about 45,000 active students, the University of Vienna is the largest and most diverse educational institution in Austria. With staff of about 7.000 academics, the University of Vienna is the largest teaching and research institution in Austria','','','','','https://www.univie.ac.at/typo3temp/_processed_/csm_Frontansicht_Flaggen_01_49e47ff8d5.jpg',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fb3T4CUGHTI',NULL,0,0,0,0,NULL,6,'2020-07-15 17:34:42');
INSERT INTO "content_record" VALUES(18,'LMU Munich','LMU Munich is consistently ranked among the world''s top 100 universities in various international ranking surveys such as the Academic Ranking of World Universities and the Times Higher Education Supplement which ranks over 1000 universities worldwide.The university ranks 16th worldwide by number of Nobel laureates.The Times Higher Education Ranking 2019 ranks LMU Munich 1st in Germany, and 32nd in the world.','','','','','https://www.uni-muenchen.de/informationen_fuer/presse/bilder/study_guide/willkommen_535_web.png',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P33KiJahJr0',NULL,0,0,0,0,NULL,13,'2020-07-15 17:34:42');
INSERT INTO "content_record" VALUES(19,'Technical University of Munich','The Technical University of Munich (TUM) (German: Technische Universität München) is a research university focused on natural sciences, engineering, medicine and social sciences concerning technology issues. It holds campuses in Munich, Garching, Freising-Weihenstephan, Heilbronn[6] and Dover, Singapore.','','','','','https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1533559592phpsYF8Oy.jpeg',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nJ-k3RpXYkI',NULL,1,0,1,0,NULL,13,'2020-07-15 17:34:42');
